&lt;li&gt;Contribute to full stack development initiatives, including backend APIs and selected frontend components using &lt;strong&gt;TypeScript&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;HTML&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;CSS&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
